ActAn Act to amend the Divorce Act, the Family Orders and Agreements Enforcement Assistance Act and the Garnishment, Attachment and Pension Diversion Act and to make consequential amendments to another Act
SubjectOrder Fixing the Days on Which Certain Provisions of that Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing (1) November 12, 2021, as the day on which subsections 73(2) to (6), section 74 and subsection 76(3) of the AN ACT TO AMEND THE DIVORCE ACT, THE FAMILY ORDERS AND GARNISHMENT, ATTACHMENT AND PENSION DIVERSION ACT AND TO MAKE CONSEQUENTIAL AMENDMENTS TO ANOTHER ACT, Chapter 16 of the Statutes of Canada, 2019, COME INTO FORCE, and (2) the day on which this Order is registered as the day on which subsections 105(1), 106(2), 111(2) to (4) and 115(3) and (5) of that Act, Chapter 16 of the Statutes of Canada, 2019, COME INTO FORCE.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2020-0075 Publication Date: 2020-12-23
